<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />You people, how long will you turn my honor into shame?</para>

<para style="q1">How long will you love that which is worthless and seek after lies?

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />But know that Yahweh sets apart the godly for himself.</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh will hear when I call to him.</para>
